In Case You Were Wondering, These Are The 20 Richest People In The World

In Case You Were Wondering, These Are The 20 Richest People In The World

Money makes the world go round, but for the most of us, there's never enough. But these people have more than enough for a few lifetimes and then some. These are the 20 richest people in the world right now.

1. Jeff Bezos

Jeff Bezos is now the richest person in the world, according to the latest annual ranking from Forbes. The Amazon founder leads with an estimated net worth of $112 billion.

Reuters

2. Bill Gates

Bill Gates is now second with an estimated net worth of $90 billion.

Reuters

3. Warren Buffett

Investing icon Warren Buffett is third with $84 billion.

Reuters

4. Bernard Arnault

LVMH Chairman and CEO Bernard Arnault is fourth with $72 billion.

Reuters

5. Mark Zuckerberg

Facebook Founder and CEO Mark Zuckerberg is fifth with $71 billion.

Reuters

6. Amancio Ortega

Inditex founder Amancio Ortega, owner of the Zara clothing chain, is sixth with $70 billion.

Reuters

7. Carlos Slim

Mexican telecommunication tycoon Carlos Slim is seventh with $67.1 billion.

Reuters

8. David Koch

David Koch and brother Charles of Koch Industries are worth $60 billion.

Reuters

9. Charles Koch

Charles Koch and brother David Koch Industries are worth $60 billion.

Politico/Forbes Collection

