10. Larry Ellison

Oracle chief Larry Ellison is tenth with $58.5 billion.

Reuters

11. Michael Bloomberg

Michael Bloomberg is worth $50 billion.

Reuters

12. Larry Page

Google co-founder Larry Page is worth $48.8 billion.

Reuters

13. Sergey Brin

Google co-founder Sergey Brin is worth $47.5 billion.

Reuters

14. Jim Walton

Jim Walton and Rob Walton of Walmart have an estimated net worth of $46.4 and $46.2 billion respectively.

Reuters

15. Rob Walton

Rob Walton and Jim Walton of Walmart have an estimated net worth of $46.4 and $46.2 billion respectively.

Reuters

16. Alice Walton

Alice Walton is worth $46 billion.

Reuters

17. Pony Ma Huateng

Tencent founder and CEO Pony Ma Huateng is worth $45.3 billion.

Reuters

18. Francoise Bettencourt-Meyers

Francoise Bettencourt-Meyers, who inherited the L'Oreal fortune following her mother's death, is worth $42.2 billion.

Reuters

19. Mukesh Ambani

Reliance Industries Limited Chairman Mukesh Ambani is worth $40.1 billion.

Reuters

20. Jack Ma

Alibaba founder and chairman Jack Ma is worth $39 billion.

